text: Great Bend USD 428 is a public unified school district headquartered in Great Bend, Kansas, United States. The district includes the communities of Great Bend and nearby rural areas.USD 428 District Map; KSDOT. ==See also== * Kansas State Department of Education * Kansas State High School Activities Association * List of high schools in Kansas * List of unified school districts in Kansas ==References== ==External links== * Category:School districts in Kansas
